Package TranRunJLiteSamples

Class Summary
ClothesMachine Simulates a wathing machine or a clothes dryer, depending on the variales that are passed to it.
Counting Implements a one-task system with three states that do nothing but count The purpose of this sample is to test the basic functions of TranRunJLite
DataLogger Data logging task for multi-motor control
DataLoggerScorbot Data logging task for multi-motor control
DataLoggerScorbot2 Data logging task for multi-motor control
JogOpInt This Class/Task connects the robot jog operations to a LabVIEW GUI This task must not run any faster than the LabVIEW GUI loop -- otherwise VERY jerky motion will result!
Main TranRunJLite Samples
Motor Create a class for a motor.
MotorSim Simulates a DC brush motor with a gearbox and load Motor inductance is ignored
MotorSimScorbot Simulates the motor of a Scorbot robot.
MotorSimScorbot2 Simulates the motor of a Scorbot robot.
MultiMotor Collects information for a set of motors so that they can be operated in a synchronized way (or, independently, if desired) This version assumes that each motor has its own simulation object.
